With 14 events in total, speed skating is the largest sport in terms of events at Beijing2022. From February 5 to 19, the speed skating events wil be held at the National Speed Skating Oval. The Dutch speed skaters have been most successful at the Olympic Games, winning a total of 16 medals out of a possible 42 at the 2018 PyeongChang Winter Games. China's Ning Zhongyan is one of the host nation's biggest gold medal hopes in Speed Skating, following an impressive World Cup series in which he claimed two golds and two silvers. Let's take one minute to learn about this sport.